Use install.sh to compile all perl modules to the temp development library
Add the path to perl's INC

export PERL5LIB=/home/m003206/projects/RNA_Tools/pdb/lib/


SWIG to add C++/C functions to perl module
############################################################################ 



1) To get the linking and included files from perl use the following
/usr/bin/perl -MExtUtils::Embed -e ldopts 
/usr/bin/perl -MExtUtils::Embed -e ccopts 


